"2019-06-09T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"我個鬼佬fd唔識中文<br />\n佢問相入面d人係唔係支持捉人去坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T05:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc9f820f8490a2aeb8ac9eff87e2b4d5bd04487","tid":1193670,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61064805fc6c485f1a786817f89fece5a3488b50","tid":1193670,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"好多人排隊扮係監獄入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"6月9號遊行嘅方針:兄弟爬山，各自努力，避免割席，拒絕篤灰，不打飛機，不傳耳語，不搞抹黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1192414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1192414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bddba35872a77d60a514c82fbad12a9ca9eb96cc","tid":1193670,"uid":37668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"香港特色遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794a0fb3afd54110d79986966daa14010ffe3e59","tid":1193670,"uid":35323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"打完咭係唔係走得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29369ed146e329375c02e9722bb2d08211855a1f","tid":1193670,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛特別警告信號現正生效 6月9日08時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過100次/禁100次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備事項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待今午遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d6aab875a74a4f064efd31ff9fbf3d93140db00","tid":1193670,"uid":143288,"like":11,"disl